title: FEAR THE WALKING DEAD - S1 - 720p - MINIMIZE THE SUCK EDIT
description:
FEAR THE WALKING DEAD - SEASON 1 - EDITED INTO A SINGLE 2h56m VIDEO

I had a theory that the reason this show sucked so much was that the produces took an okay 3 episode show and stretched it out into a 6 episode monstrosity.

Once I cut out over 2 HOURS of bloated garbage from the show, I ended up with an okay zombie show. 

Watch it and let me know what you thought of it at @Max_G_Force on twitter.
